narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: D4c of Texas PLLC is a Clinic/Center, Dental provider based in Austin, TX. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $75.3M in Medicaid payments across 2.5M claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $75.3M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
